with a beauty.

00:39:59.760 --> 00:40:00.440
♪ The secret of meeting you ♪

00:40:00.440 --> 00:40:01.570
How inappropriate!

00:40:03.590 --> 00:40:05.010
These are compliments.

00:40:06.710 --> 00:40:08.240
Whatever floats your boat.

00:40:09.540 --> 00:40:10.330
An Xian, clean this up.

